gw.api.address

Interface AddressFillable

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    AddressAutofillable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Address, AddressAutofillEntity, PolicyLocationSummary

    public interface AddressFillable
    Interface for an object holding Address data used for auto complete and auto fill. Corresponds to fields defined for AddressAutofillable entity. Customer added fields will be accessed reflectively.
    Author:
    jfehrle
